title: How Women’s Products Are Made Differently?
description:
A new era of sports innovation is here; and it’s built for her. 

Across football, rugby, and trail running, adidas is working side by side with female athletes, researchers, and designers to reimagine what performance gear can be...not adapted but purposefully engineered. From the lab to the pitch, this represents more than a product breakthrough it’s a statement of intent. 

Made for her needs, shaped for her game and built for her performance.

This is the story of innovation shaped by real needs, real feedback, and real progress; told by the athletes, designers, and leaders driving the future of sport. 

Rooted in 75 years of legacy, we continue to shape the industry. 

Find out more:
Sparkfusion: https://news.adidas.com/football/adidas-launches-f50-sparkfusion---a-boot-built-by-and-for-women-s-football-players/s/7a72e410-249a-4f43-afd5-cbf3222f5f60

title: Anything But Clubs with Collin Morikawa, Rose Zhang and Nick Dunlap
description:
Get ready for golf like you've never seen it before! We challenged PGA pros Collin Morikawa, Nick Dunlap, and LPGA pro Rose Zhang to the ultimate "Anything But Clubs" golf challenge. 

Forget your drivers and putters – on this par 3, these pros are forced to use everything from a baseball bat to a ping pong paddle to get to the hole! Watch as they strategize, struggle, and somehow sink shots with the most unexpected equipment. 

Who will master the madness and take home the win? You won't believe what happens when golf's best are stripped of their usual tools.

title: Carsen Edwards - A Family Thing | adidas
description:
He’s a star point guard at FC Bayern Basketball. EuroLeague top scorer with 20.7 PPG. 2024–25 All-EuroLeague First Team. German National Champion. German Cup winner. Finals MVP. Carsen Edwards is stacking accolades - but where does he find his strength when the lights go off? 
 
In this intimate short documentary, we step beyond the hardwood and into the heart of Carsen’s world. From family childhood memories to life overseas in Germany, Carsen opens up about the role his family - especially his big brother - has played in shaping who he is, both as an athlete and a person.
 
With unseen behind-the-scenes footage, “Carsen Edwards – A Family Thing” offers a rare look into the private life of a pro basketball player, showing us how family isn’t just part of the journey – it is the journey.

title: How Messi and Mahomes Motivate Each Other to Reach New Heights
description:
Someone’s pushing Patrick Mahomes buttons.

adidas athletes Patrick Mahomes and​ LeoMessi⁩ push each other forward in this new film reminding us that when you’ve got someone by your side - You Got This.

Even the world's greatest athletes need someone to support them, to motivate them, to push them, to believe in them. In some cases, being around other greats, are the best way to have fun, to loosen up, to lift their mood, to get even better.

Having someone to push you can mean the difference between improvement and stagnation. Between feeling bogged down or like maybe your best is still ahead of you and anything is possible.  

When someone you respect pushes the yardstick forward and challenges you to come with them, you know #yougotthis

title: 7 Beginner Weight Training Exercises For Women | adidas
description:
Feel strong and confident in the gym with a beginner weightlifting routine for women, featuring seven full body exercises led by strength coach Britany Williams. 

If you're feeling nervous to start a new weight training routine in the gym, we’re here to make it simple. 

With a mix of dumbbells, fixed weight bars, and standard machines, you can do all seven of these moves for a full-body women’s strength workout, or just pick a few to get comfortable with the flow of a new gym. 

The Exercises: 
1. Dumbbell Goblet Squat (1:03) 
2. Dumbbell Chest Press (2:02) 
3. RDL (3:31) 
4. Seated Shoulder Press (5:01) 
5. Deadbug (6:40) 
6. Bent Over Row (7:49) 
7. Leg Extension (9:10) 

Check out the full story on the adidas blog: https://www.adidas.com/us/blog/beginner-weight-training-for-women-7-exercises-to-try

Find out more at http://www.adidas.com

Aitana Bonmatí by her friend Maria.
She’s a Ballon D’Or winner and globally recognized as one of the greatest footballers of all time. So who does Aitani Bonmatí look to when she needs belief, support and inspiration? Meet her friend, Maria.

In this exclusive new film, see Aitana through Maria’s eyes. As they talk about the very real pressures of being a sports star and role model, walk the streets of Aitana’s hometown, and play a relaxed game of football with friends, Maria shows us a story only a friend could tell.
